data.description: Welcome to 527 Ansley Forest! Situated in the back cul-de-sac of the quiet Ansley Forest neighborhood located conveniently close to GA-78, this lovely two story contemporary build has it all: a secluded back yard with horse farm views, privacy fencing, heated & cooled detached shop, large carport with concrete pad, newer HVAC systems, generous lot size, newer roof, and a flooring budget set aside for its new owner to choose what fits their style! I assure you that you will not be disappointed with this home, so be sure to book your showing today before the market gets too competitive!
